INSERT INTO `diary` VALUES ('1', '走村串寨寻过往——双飞自驾黔东南（七日游）', '时至2017年12月下旬儿子年假还没歇，与我们商议全家出游，提议自驾 漠河 ，因', '安徽', 'http://localhost:8081/image/diary/1/1.webp', '<h2><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">开场白</span></h2><p data-seq=\"282167525\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">时至2017年12月下旬儿子年假还没歇，与我们商议全家出游，提议自驾&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"漠河\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10427.html\" target=\"_blank\">漠河</a>&nbsp;，因恐道路冰雪被我们老两口儿否决；我们提出到&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"武夷山\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10039.html\" target=\"_blank\">武夷山</a>&nbsp;，儿子又恐&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"福建\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12871.html\" target=\"_blank\">福建</a>&nbsp;朋友知道酒桌乏力；到&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"泰国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10083.html\" target=\"_blank\">泰国</a>&nbsp;略显仓促；最后我提议双飞自驾&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;，大家一拍即合。于是儿子向领导递交休假报告并当即网购了往返机票，我开始做功课订出行计划。<br>12月27日我在蚂蜂窝提出&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;7天游的行程计划征求意见请求，得到了两位蜂蜂的热情帮助。这时我马上私信&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;自由行的资深玩儿家蜂友——云贵川，请求得到他的指导和帮助，云贵川兄不厌其烦经过频繁私信沟通，终于指导我完成了行动纲领和计划。在这里向云贵川兄深表谢意，对回答我问题的“画出彩虹”、“骑着毛驴去&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"西藏\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12700.html\" target=\"_blank\">西藏</a>&nbsp;”二位蜂友一并致谢。<br>12月29日儿子的休假得到批准，即刻进入行前准备，2018第一次行动计划将在元旦黎明前开始。<br></span></p><h2><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">为什么是黔东南</span></h2><p data-seq=\"282363952\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">我现在是 “看东西越来越远，尿尿越来越近；坐着打瞌睡，躺下睡不着；眼前的事记不住，过去的事忘不了”，小时候屋里昏暗的煤油灯、蜡烛，在农村劳动时喝过的井水睡的土炕，冬天家家取暖做饭的煤球炉子，夏天光着屁股在河沟子里游泳，冬天穿裤腰到胳肢窝的大棉裤……。只要有人跟我聊儿时的事情就异常兴奋，有如“江水滔滔不绝于耳熟能详”（央视名嘴语法），惧新恋旧，整个儿一个衰老的节奏！<br>现在出门旅游由于过度商业化大多是花钱买热闹，“去了还不错，不去也正好儿”，让人哭笑两便。<br>忽忽然，听人说起&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵州\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14103.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵州</a>&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;却让我的小心脏为之怦然！<br>有书为证：<br><a data-kw=\"贵州\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14103.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵州</a>&nbsp;,是&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"中国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;唯一没有平原的省份,戏称“地无三尺平”。其中人数较多的两个少数民族苗族与侗族,基本集中在&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;一带。早在 1992年,&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;就与&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"西藏\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12700.html\" target=\"_blank\">西藏</a>&nbsp;一起被列入&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"亚洲\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html\" target=\"_blank\">亚洲</a>&nbsp;仅有 的两个“回归自然、返璞归真”的最佳旅游胜地。后来,&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;又被联合国世界乡土文化保护基金会确认为全球18个“人与自然保护圈”之 一。<br>一百年前的旅行者离开故乡时,随处可见参差多态的地域文化;而今,人们似乎只能在某些遗漏之处才能找到渴望的原始景观。“山地”就是这 样的遗漏之处。“山排斥伟大的历史,排斥由它带来的坏处和好处。”<br>在&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;,恰恰是无穷的山地延缓了当代文明与旅游的步伐,造就了这最后的“净土”，用小聚落的变化缓慢的生存方式世代繁衍。 所以,当其他地区进入当代城市文明时,&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;大山深处许多村寨就像桃花源一般仍然留驻着过去的生活景观。<br><a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;是2016年度 《&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"纽约\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10579.html\" target=\"_blank\">纽约</a>&nbsp;时报》 推荐的世界上52个最值得到访的旅游目的地之一。推荐理由是：“正宗的&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"中国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;山地部落，尚未被大众旅游覆盖”。<br><br>得嘞，这些已经足够，什么话儿都不用说了，就是它！<br></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">正篇</span></h2><p data-seq=\"283633089\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">以前，&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;交通闭塞，从&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵阳</a>&nbsp;到&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黎平\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63082.html\" target=\"_blank\">黎平</a>&nbsp;坐车要两天。大山深处的交通不便使村寨与外面的世界隔绝，当地少数民族自给自足的生活方式和文化传统不受外来侵袭而得以保护传承，但也伴随着物质的匮乏贫穷与落后。现在无处不达的高速路，高铁，村村通、互联网、智能手机、青壮年走出大山到&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"大城\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16107.html\" target=\"_blank\">大城</a>&nbsp;市读书、打工，迅速改变着他们的命运，也改变着那里千百年来不变的生活方式。市场经济的浪潮席卷之处，如果不去人为的特意的大力保护，传统文化行将荡然无存。青山绿水就是金山&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"银山\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145107.html\" target=\"_blank\">银山</a>&nbsp;，精准扶贫一定要精心保护环境和精心保护少数民族的传统文化，千万别弄巧成拙精准破坏。<br>一切都在变，那里也不会幸免，商业化的脚步正在迈出或正在筹谋之中，跟我一样恋旧的朋友，想去那里一定要趁早儿，不然就像在&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"北京\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;找胡同及胡同文化——对不起了您内，没啦！现在那些胡同游都是糊弄游客的假招子赝品。<br><br>当我整理此行的照片时，仿佛又回到过去的时光，把木心 的《从前慢 》抄录于此，沏上一壶茶，慢慢地回味……<br>“记得早先少年时<br>大家诚诚恳恳<br>说一句是一句<br>清早上火车站<br>长街黑暗无行人<br>卖豆浆的小店冒着热气<br>从前的日色变得慢<br>车马邮件都慢<br>一生只够爱一个人<br>从前的锁也好看<br>钥匙精美有样子<br>你锁了<br>人家就懂了”</span></p><h2><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">简况</span></h2><p data-seq=\"282206851\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">★人员： 夫、妻、儿<br>★总天数：7天6晚（1月1日——1月7日）<br>★自驾总行程：1200KM<br>★总花费：10498元 人均：3500元<br>其中：<br>机票4680（45%），租车费1535（15%），高速费590（6%）.，油费651（6%），存车费50（/），<br>住宿费1168（11%），门票364（3%），餐费1259（12%），其他200（2%）<br></span></p><h2><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">日程</span></h2><p data-seq=\"282265940\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">第一天：（早&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"北京\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;飞）&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵阳</a>&nbsp;→&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\">肇兴</a>&nbsp;侗寨 自驾280公里<br>第二天：&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\">肇兴</a>&nbsp;侗寨→述洞村 自驾90公里<br>第三天：述洞村→地扪村→腊洞→大利村 自驾70公里<br>第四天：大利村→西江千户苗寨 自驾210公里<br>第五天：西江千户苗寨→黄果树 自驾350公里<br>第六天：黄果树→&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵阳</a>&nbsp;自驾150公里<br>第七天：&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵阳</a>&nbsp;→机场（午飞&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"北京\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;） 自驾15公里<br></span></p><h2><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">天气</span></h2><p data-seq=\"283962943\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">值得注意的是&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;阴冷的天气，1月初温度白天6-7℃，夜里2-3℃,几乎见不到阳光，屋里比外边还冷，专门欺负冬天习惯屋内有供暖的北方人，那种冷是由内而外的，现在想想都战栗。建议带上羽绒衣裤,在没有空调的村寨客栈夜里穿着睡觉 。<br><a data-kw=\"贵州\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14103.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵州</a>&nbsp;山地多，小气候多，一山有四季，十里不同天，但我们在&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;的几天，天天下雨，而且是几百里内都同天，处处下雨。都说出门必备雨具，我看未必，那里的雨时大时小似有似无，你打开伞它停了，你收起伞，一会儿就淋你个湿，但请放心不等让你成落汤鸡，它又停了。所以嫌麻烦就不用带雨具. 我的伞始终在旅行箱里懒得拿出来，外面穿个冲锋衣足矣.。带相机的就把冲锋衣拉锁拉开一半，随时放进拿出。<br></span></p><h2><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">第一天元旦 自驾行程280公里</span></h2><p data-seq=\"282416851\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">当日活动概要：<br><a data-kw=\"北京\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;国际机场飞&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵阳</a>&nbsp;龙洞堡机场，11点30&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵阳</a>&nbsp;提车12点自驾下午4:50抵&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黎平\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63082.html\" target=\"_blank\">黎平</a>&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\">肇兴</a>&nbsp;侗寨，住“溪舍•山堂”客栈，游&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\">肇兴</a>&nbsp;侗寨夜景，逛街。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155428.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A9/wKgBEFpW54uAOSA5AAc_13nWXlg33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A9/wKgBEFpW54uAOSA5AAc_13nWXlg33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A9/wKgBEFpW54uAOSA5AAc_13nWXlg33.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155428\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"7730773\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/7730773.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肯塔基州机场</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282398724\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">2018年的第一天，我们天没亮就来到了首都机场T3航站楼，将在天上迎接新年的第一缕阳光。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155429.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AA/wKgBEFpW54yAfoNtAAhSgvmxsm077.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AA/wKgBEFpW54yAfoNtAAhSgvmxsm077.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AA/wKgBEFpW54yAfoNtAAhSgvmxsm077.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155429\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"6984849\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6984849.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">龙洞堡国际机场</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282399293\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">10点50分来到&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵阳</a>&nbsp;龙洞堡机场负一楼的“一嗨租车”，如约提车。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281221069.html\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #F3F3F3;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/74/2F/wKgBEFpXIR2AZm9dAAFdQ667e3859.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/74/2F/wKgBEFpXIR2AZm9dAAFdQ667e3859.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/74/2F/wKgBEFpXIR2AZm9dAAFdQ667e3859.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281221069\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></span></span></span></span></span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282402601\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">百度导航走起</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281318575.html\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #F3F3F3;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CE/75/wKgBEFpXde-Afvl7AAgDtGG1vmQ32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CE/75/wKgBEFpXde-Afvl7AAgDtGG1vmQ32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CE/75/wKgBEFpXde-Afvl7AAgDtGG1vmQ32.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281318575\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></span></span></span></span></span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282402781\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">12点整 开始自驾行程，驾着“标致3008”上路，人在车上，心在远方。<br>（眼尖的蜂友发现后视镜里的司机合着眼睛，涉嫌疲劳驾驶耶。孩儿他娘的抓拍能力比电子眼还厉害！）</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155430.html\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #F3F3F3;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AA/wKgBEFpW54yACmdTAAbuLxN1pVQ08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AA/wKgBEFpW54yACmdTAAbuLxN1pVQ08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AA/wKgBEFpW54yACmdTAAbuLxN1pVQ08.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155430\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></span></span></span></span></span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282402863\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">既然几多期许在大山深处，不管山高路远，只顾雨雾兼程。<br>“老夫聊发少年狂，左牵黄，右擎苍，锦帽貂裘，千骑卷平冈……”。按蜂友“点燃一支烟”的说法，咱也豪迈一把，驱赶一下很长时间以来笼罩心头的抑郁。<br>　</span></p><p><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/83/3F/wKgBEFqXw_KAaskPAAR3Wlvsz3874.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" title=\"① 肇兴侗寨\" alt=\"① 肇兴侗寨\" class=\"fr-fin\"></p><p data-seq=\"282403383\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴</span></a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">&nbsp;侗寨，位于&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"贵州\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14103.html\" target=\"_blank\">贵州</a>&nbsp;省&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黔东南\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10381.html\" target=\"_blank\">黔东南</a>&nbsp;苗族侗族自治州&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"黎平\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63082.html\" target=\"_blank\">黎平</a>&nbsp;县东南部，是全国最大的侗族村寨之一，素有\"侗乡第一寨\"之美誉。2005年被《&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"中国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;国家地理》评选为\"&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"中国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;最美的六大乡村古镇\"之一，2007年被《时尚旅游》和&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"美国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10062.html\" target=\"_blank\">美国</a>&nbsp;《国家地理》共同评选为\"全球最具诱惑力的33个旅游目的地\"之一。&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\">肇兴</a>&nbsp;侗寨全为陆姓侗族，分为五大房族，分居五个自然片区，当地称之为\"团\"。分为仁团、义团、礼团、智团、信团五团。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155431.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AB/wKgBEFpW542ALWzvAAozUpID3Fo33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AB/wKgBEFpW542ALWzvAAozUpID3Fo33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AB/wKgBEFpW542ALWzvAAozUpID3Fo33.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155431\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282404239\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">4点40分在景区大门外车被横杆拦下，购票40元一张门票（淡季价）继续行车，4点50分存车后进入&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\">肇兴</a>&nbsp;侗寨。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155416.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54GAVZAPAAjnM7TPqss60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54GAVZAPAAjnM7TPqss60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54GAVZAPAAjnM7TPqss60.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155416\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282408816\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">行李箱暂放在车里，徒步进寨找住处。寨子里沿着大街不时有免费电瓶车方便游客乘坐。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155418.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54OATKbuAAjwJnbMkCU97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54OATKbuAAjwJnbMkCU97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54OATKbuAAjwJnbMkCU97.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155418\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282409254\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">路遇信团鼓楼很多当地人头戴白色&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"包头\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11574.html\" target=\"_blank\">包头</a>&nbsp;疑似丧事活动。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155421.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A4/wKgBEFpW54WAQGRGAAcjAf0h-FU53.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A4/wKgBEFpW54WAQGRGAAcjAf0h-FU53.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A4/wKgBEFpW54WAQGRGAAcjAf0h-FU53.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155421\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"281362768\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">信团鼓楼。侗族人始终相信鼓楼可以镇寨，给村寨带来稳&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"固安\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/140608.html\" target=\"_blank\">固安</a>&nbsp;宁和人丁兴旺。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155422.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A4/wKgBEFpW54aAScB7AAlaJ9cxjQI83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A4/wKgBEFpW54aAScB7AAlaJ9cxjQI83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A4/wKgBEFpW54aAScB7AAlaJ9cxjQI83.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155422\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"283086211\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">一直走到寨子的东边见到徒步&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"堂安\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21254.html\" target=\"_blank\">堂安</a>&nbsp;寨的小路<br></span></p><h2><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">（花絮一） 小掌柜出口伤客</span></h2><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/293961098.html\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #F3F3F3;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/85/65/wKgBEFqSOr2AM7sBAAB2u8Bx6mY88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/85/65/wKgBEFqSOr2AM7sBAAB2u8Bx6mY88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/85/65/wKgBEFqSOr2AM7sBAAB2u8Bx6mY88.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"293961098\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></span></span></span></span></span></a></p><p data-seq=\"293961233\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴</span></a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">&nbsp;青定阁位于&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"肇兴\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10103.html\" target=\"_blank\">肇兴</a>&nbsp;古镇礼团鼓楼旁，距离小镇主要街道咫尺之遥,掌柜不是本地人小伙儿年龄不大外形挺斯文的，在京我与之通过话，看了他的家庭房感觉不错，报价300元,我还价280元，其实让不让价无所谓.，因为寨子里几乎没有游客，讨价还价再正常不过。小伙子一句:：“我最讨厌讨价还价” 原本和谐的气氛顿时全无，“小伙子你怎么这么讲话”？“我给的是最低价，‘讨厌’是不喜欢没有别的意思”。尽管他作了各种解释.，‘讨厌’这个词儿对客人是非常不礼貌的,，让价咱也不住！但愿这只是南北语言文化差异，我这&nbsp;<a data-kw=\"北京\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;老炮儿理儿多，买卖不成情意在，掌柜应该使用文明用语，如果遇到几个吃生米儿的你这是讨打的节奏。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/301459612.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AC/60/wKgBEFqtIuKAKwpyAAK58cH6SGc43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AC/60/wKgBEFqtIuKAKwpyAAK58cH6SGc43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AC/60/wKgBEFqtIuKAKwpyAAK58cH6SGc43.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"301459612\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282411083\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">一路考察了N多旅店客栈最后我们选择了“溪舍~山堂”一家性价比很高软硬件都不错的客栈住下，很超值。<br>小提示：不要相信所谓点评，我们考察了几家得分高的客栈徒有其名，软硬都不行只有要价高。只要不是旺季最好多看几家，总有一款适合的。<br></span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/284869497.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/A1/10/wKgBEFpptlaAENWzAAn7tdku4PU70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/A1/10/wKgBEFpptlaAENWzAAn7tdku4PU70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/A1/10/wKgBEFpptlaAENWzAAn7tdku4PU70.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"284869497\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282412833\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">仁团鼓楼风雨桥</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155781.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/10/wKgBEFpW6EmAJcxLAA0vreLYHiY91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/10/wKgBEFpW6EmAJcxLAA0vreLYHiY91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/10/wKgBEFpW6EmAJcxLAA0vreLYHiY91.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155781\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282412034\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">仁团鼓楼夜景</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155804.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/1C/wKgBEFpW6FyAQj7QAAuNqpkUAok26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/1C/wKgBEFpW6FyAQj7QAAuNqpkUAok26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/1C/wKgBEFpW6FyAQj7QAAuNqpkUAok26.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155804\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"281362808\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">仁团花桥夜景。花桥也叫风雨桥，侗家人始终相信花桥可以阻隔外来的邪恶，给整个村寨带来风调雨顺。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281156483.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/87/wKgBEFpW6RiAIEAGAAs3mkS6Xhs47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/87/wKgBEFpW6RiAIEAGAAs3mkS6Xhs47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/87/wKgBEFpW6RiAIEAGAAs3mkS6Xhs47.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281156483\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282412157\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">信团鼓楼在大街边烤火的人比其它鼓楼多，众人施柴火焰高，印证了“火大无湿柴”。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155795.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/16/wKgBEFpW6FWAdUdWAAlOrGtB6VQ04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/16/wKgBEFpW6FWAdUdWAAlOrGtB6VQ04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/16/wKgBEFpW6FWAdUdWAAlOrGtB6VQ04.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155795\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"281362653\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">礼团鼓楼下只有一位老人烤火我凑上去拉上几句，老人已90岁高龄，看上去还很健康。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281156486.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/89/wKgBEFpW6RuARVbdAAm7SbeVMiQ12.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/89/wKgBEFpW6RuARVbdAAm7SbeVMiQ12.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/36/89/wKgBEFpW6RuARVbdAAm7SbeVMiQ12.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281156486\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282414595\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">街边几个侗家妇女围坐在一起跟着视频哼唱侗歌。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155417.html\"><img src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54KAILMRAAqyDYZRenM43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54KAILMRAAqyDYZRenM43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/A1/wKgBEFpW54KAILMRAAqyDYZRenM43.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155417\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"283376513\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">多家当地土特产店铺遍布街两边。</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281231890.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/7E/D6/wKgBEFpXKP6AF8UrAAm_Sp8u-Ks23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/7E/D6/wKgBEFpXKP6AF8UrAAm_Sp8u-Ks23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/7E/D6/wKgBEFpXKP6AF8UrAAm_Sp8u-Ks23.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281231890\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282414508\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">街摊夜市</span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10381/scenery_8289454/281155434.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AC/wKgBEFpW55CAMc6tAAsmecs4bTQ88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AC/wKgBEFpW55CAMc6tAAsmecs4bTQ88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/35/AC/wKgBEFpW55CAMc6tAAsmecs4bTQ88.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"281155434\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" data-poiid=\"11170\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/11170.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times; color: #000000; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">肇兴侗寨</span></a></p><p data-seq=\"282610762\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span data-fr-verified=\"true\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times New Roman,Times;\">各种各样的串串勾着路人的馋虫<br>是时候了，肚子咕咕的叫着又来指挥大脑了。</span></p>', '4', '特别策划', '1', '2022-06-09', '10', '1000', '一个人', '2022-06-05 17:00:42');
INSERT INTO `diary` VALUES ('2', '游者乐山', '冥冥之中自有天意', '安徽', 'http://localhost:8081/image/diary/2/2.webp', '<p data-seq=\"1116096551\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">冥冥之中自有天意。记得两年前的夏天，我们几乎是被所有朋友抛弃，他们都各回各娘家，带着孩子各找各妈。已习惯暑假出游的我和肥妻，在阳光灿烂的日子惶惶不可终日，为了不辜负这美好夏天，于是快速圈定<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"峨眉山\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10143.html\" target=\"_blank\">峨眉山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，然后疯狂做攻略，路线慢慢成型，想象中旅途的欢乐慢慢弥漫脑海。处在幻想与现实难分真假的我，手机突然传来远回<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"西宁\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10800.html\" target=\"_blank\">西宁</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>娘家的胖嫂魔性的声音：“暑假决定去哪玩？”我：“我们去<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"峨眉山\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10143.html\" target=\"_blank\">峨眉山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>。”胖嫂：“来<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"西宁\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10800.html\" target=\"_blank\">西宁</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>吧，青甘大环线，连绵十几里的油菜花海，茶卡盐湖。”“我们去<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>峨眉。”“有姥爷车随你开，有手抓羊。。。”“我们去<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>。。。”“去<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"张掖\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11340.html\" target=\"_blank\">张掖</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>看七彩丹霞。。。”“我们去。。。！！！”谁叫胖嫂的声音那么有魔性呢？谁叫七彩丹霞是我立为今生必去的两个地方之一呢？所以我们马上就放弃了抵抗，青甘大环线转了一圈，最后也没失望，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"青海\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12788.html\" target=\"_blank\">青海</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>至今是我觉得最好的旅游省份。今年的情形与两年前一样，我们也做好了<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"峨眉山\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10143.html\" target=\"_blank\">峨眉山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>的行程，于是我微信胖嫂：“今年一起去<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>峨眉玩吧！”“我们回<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"西宁\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10800.html\" target=\"_blank\">西宁</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>了。”“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>有火锅。。。”“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"西宁\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10800.html\" target=\"_blank\">西宁</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>天气宜人。”“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>有火锅。。。”“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"西宁\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10800.html\" target=\"_blank\">西宁</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>有。。。”“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>有火锅。。。”“好吧，我们去<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"成都\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>汇合你们。”这世界上的事没什么是一顿火锅解决不了的，如果有，就两顿，实在不行就三四五六七八顿！看苍天饶过谁！！！</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116103856.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/28/1F/CoUBUl8_36OAFq8kAAmNh5_1tog644.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/28/1F/CoUBUl8_36OAFq8kAAmNh5_1tog644.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/28/1F/CoUBUl8_36OAFq8kAAmNh5_1tog644.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116103856\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"1116103866\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">七月二十九下午两点，微微细雨中我和肥妻到了<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11273.html\" data-kw=\"乐山\" target=\"_blank\">乐山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，航班的误点搞得我心浮气躁兼饥肠辘辘，所以叶婆婆是我这时最想见的人，不，最想见和最想吃的是她的钵钵鸡，当一大盘钵钵鸡摆在我和肥妻面前时，上面那一堆略显凌乱但娇艳无比的竹签，早已晃得我眼花缭乱和口水横流，罪恶的双爪迫不及待的伸出，还没抓起竹签，嘴巴就早早张开，美味的销魂让我把在酒店等候的胖哥胖嫂抛到九天之外，忘了跟他们说一下我们到了，插一句，胖嫂不胖，之所以这样称呼，完全是因为胖哥，胖哥是真胖！其实这也怪不得我，一来实在太饿，二来我碰上美食就像英雄遇到美人，黄鼠狼见到。。。呸！呸！是狗见到。。。不！不！是猫见到了鱼。。。好吧，反正是情难自控，天性所然。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116110059.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/57/CoUBUl8_4FmAZ0kMAA6cM64gZhA867.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/57/CoUBUl8_4FmAZ0kMAA6cM64gZhA867.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/57/CoUBUl8_4FmAZ0kMAA6cM64gZhA867.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116110059\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116110060.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/5C/CoUBUl8_4FuARgSiAAzbSstfCv8232.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/5C/CoUBUl8_4FuARgSiAAzbSstfCv8232.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/5C/CoUBUl8_4FuARgSiAAzbSstfCv8232.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116110060\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116110061.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/62/CoUBUl8_4F2AImuyAAp8tfLYq3I451.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/62/CoUBUl8_4F2AImuyAAp8tfLYq3I451.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/62/CoUBUl8_4F2AImuyAAp8tfLYq3I451.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116110061\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"1116110065\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">天气预报说这两天都有雨，趁着小雨时下时停，所以和胖哥汇合后就直奔<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11273.html\" data-kw=\"乐山\" target=\"_blank\">乐山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>大佛。我们没有选择坐游船观看这种没有一点技术含量的路线，而是直接爬山，近距离仰望亲近小时候电影里深刻脑海的<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/25645.html\" data-kw=\"凌云\" target=\"_blank\">凌云</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>大佛。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116110590.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/C7/CoUBUl8_4JOAcgVAAA8YdZOFWKI799.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/C7/CoUBUl8_4JOAcgVAAA8YdZOFWKI799.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/29/C7/CoUBUl8_4JOAcgVAAA8YdZOFWKI799.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116110590\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"1116110592\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">刚上山，文人骚客留下的书法石刻还没欣赏几幅，又下起了小雨，紧张的肥妻连忙拿出雨衣让我穿上，我当然拒绝，穿着雨衣拍照一点都不方便，而且只是毛毛雨，雨中登山，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13519.html\" data-kw=\"临江\" target=\"_blank\">临江</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>挥手，这种情景不常遇见，廉颇老矣，尚能指点<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12393.html\" data-kw=\"江山\" target=\"_blank\">江山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，这感觉好得不要不要的！没多久，雨停了，兴致一下子又仿佛跌到低点，想起过往种种淋雨的情景，又想起吾友蒋捷的那首《虞美人》：少年听雨歌楼上。。。一时间诗兴大发，模仿好友的词，也作一首以抒胸怀：“少年淋雨马路上，女友真混账；壮年淋雨搬砖中，双眼迷离摇摆就西风。 而今淋雨<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11273.html\" data-kw=\"乐山\" target=\"_blank\">乐山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>下，鬓已斑斑也，悲欢离合烟云轻，一任阶前打脸到天明。”不要跟我杠什么平仄，不要跟我杠什么韵味，如果不是一直淋雨多，脑子进水满得都流出来，我早就真正的指点<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12393.html\" data-kw=\"江山\" target=\"_blank\">江山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>了，还会是现在这种资深猥琐油腻大叔抓住为数不多的机会装腔作势？唉，再过几年，连大叔都不是了，要自动进阶成糟老头了，是我说得太多了吗？怎么脸上全是雨水？？</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111049.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/3C/CoUBUl8_4NqAG27VABDe17CJuQ4371.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/3C/CoUBUl8_4NqAG27VABDe17CJuQ4371.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/3C/CoUBUl8_4NqAG27VABDe17CJuQ4371.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111049\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111050.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/41/CoUBUl8_4N2AdDxcABDxIG089sE669.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/41/CoUBUl8_4N2AdDxcABDxIG089sE669.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/41/CoUBUl8_4N2AdDxcABDxIG089sE669.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111050\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111623.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2C/38/CoUBUl8_4diAFlImAAYw3uvV6HM925.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2C/38/CoUBUl8_4diAFlImAAYw3uvV6HM925.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2C/38/CoUBUl8_4diAFlImAAYw3uvV6HM925.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111623\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"1116111625\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><br>走着走着，就到了<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11273.html\" data-kw=\"乐山\" target=\"_blank\">乐山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>大佛头部旁边的山上，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11273.html\" data-kw=\"乐山\" target=\"_blank\">乐山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>大佛有“佛是一座山，山是一座佛”的美誉，所以佛像头部就是山顶。我站在佛头旁边，与佛像一个方向，模仿着佛像的神态，双眼微睁，嘴角微开，如拈花般似笑非笑，当然是没有一点神似，更没有普度众生的胸怀和能力。面前是岷江、青衣江、<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16422.html\" data-kw=\"大渡河\" target=\"_blank\">大渡河</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63836.html\" data-kw=\"三江\" target=\"_blank\">三江</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>汇聚的地方，可能是这两天下雨的原因，土黄色的河水湍急，浊浪滔天，惊涛拍岸的声音响彻山间，而我却没感到丝毫的震动，登高山而小江河说的可能就是这种情况吧，人处于的高度就是眼界的高度也是心胸的高度，这话一点都没错，很多道理谁都明白，但不是谁都做得到！</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111156.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/82/CoUBUl8_4QOAHgjkABBuOWvCRgo854.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/82/CoUBUl8_4QOAHgjkABBuOWvCRgo854.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/82/CoUBUl8_4QOAHgjkABBuOWvCRgo854.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111156\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111157.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/86/CoUBUl8_4QaAce5tAArWtPN1Mzo822.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/86/CoUBUl8_4QaAce5tAArWtPN1Mzo822.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/86/CoUBUl8_4QaAce5tAArWtPN1Mzo822.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111157\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111158.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/8A/CoUBUl8_4QeAUFa4AAY-6dGnwd8701.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/8A/CoUBUl8_4QeAUFa4AAY-6dGnwd8701.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/8A/CoUBUl8_4QeAUFa4AAY-6dGnwd8701.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111158\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111159.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/92/CoUBUl8_4QuAIwMuAA5yNL9UI0s517.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/92/CoUBUl8_4QuAIwMuAA5yNL9UI0s517.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/92/CoUBUl8_4QuAIwMuAA5yNL9UI0s517.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111159\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111160.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/98/CoUBUl8_4Q6Af9fwABAtj669nX8124.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/98/CoUBUl8_4Q6Af9fwABAtj669nX8124.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2A/98/CoUBUl8_4Q6Af9fwABAtj669nX8124.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111160\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111584.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2B/EA/CoUBUl8_4bOAYm-DAAxHCTJf1Kk800.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2B/EA/CoUBUl8_4bOAYm-DAAxHCTJf1Kk800.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2B/EA/CoUBUl8_4bOAYm-DAAxHCTJf1Kk800.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111584\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/11273/scenery_20684041/1116111585.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2B/F0/CoUBUl8_4bWAOc8TAA0JQfOa7T0575.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2B/F0/CoUBUl8_4bWAOc8TAA0JQfOa7T0575.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s16/M00/2B/F0/CoUBUl8_4bWAOc8TAA0JQfOa7T0575.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1116111585\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"1116111166\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><br>我一副众人皆醒我独装得道高人的模样，隐约的气势唬得小伙伴只能站在一旁等候，一番云游天外之后，实在装不下去了，才慢慢的前行。沿山开凿的小路狭窄陡峭，肥妻对于这座修于唐朝开元年间的<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17298.html\" data-kw=\"弥勒\" target=\"_blank\">弥勒</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>大佛没有过多的提问，可能是做攻略时有所了解，又或者是去年暑假在<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15228.html\" data-kw=\"嵩山\" target=\"_blank\">嵩山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>和<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10094.html\" data-kw=\"洛阳\" target=\"_blank\">洛阳</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>时得到了恶补，更多可能是现在问的再多也记不住，明天该忘的不该忘的都会忘记！来到大佛脚下，离汹涌的江水不到一米，浪声震耳欲聋，才感到这奔腾的气势，再仰望大佛，除了雄伟、庄严、威武之外便找不到什么更好的形容词了。人在滔滔江边，弱小如草芥，站在巍峨大佛下，渺小如蝼蚁！高度真的决定眼界！膜拜之后登九曲栈道，每一个转折我略作停留，看看大佛，又看看大江，每升高一层，心境也随之豁然开朗一些，到达最高点，王八之气油然而生，高度真的决定心胸！</p>', '4', '特别策划', '1', '2022-06-01', '10', '1000', '一个人', '2022-06-08 01:00:15');
INSERT INTO `diary` VALUES ('3', '小西湘记', '普天同庆日，霍霍创新高。', '安徽', 'http://localhost:8081/image/diary/3/3.webp', '<p data-seq=\"879469457\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">普天同庆日，霍霍创新高。这次国庆假期祸害的是朋友的朋友欧阳先生一家，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"中国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>好邻居赵老师的儿子的同学的妈妈就是欧阳太太，关系一点都不曲折复杂。我一向对艺术工作者比较敬重，欧阳先生夫妇都是画画的高人，我称其为先生，不是一般客套的称谓，本来想叫大师，但现在大师二字贬义巨大，有羞辱成分，叫老师吧，也不好，毕竟如今阿猫阿狗都互称老师，导致老师烂大街了，在我心目中只有教书育人才能称其老师，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"比如\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63538.html\" target=\"_blank\">比如</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>邻居赵老师。敌人的敌人是不是朋友我不知道，但朋友的朋友绝对是我的朋友，在赵老师家初次见面的晚餐，三杯吐言诺，眼花耳热后我就把欧阳先生当作了朋友中的真朋友，至于他把不把我当朋友，那是他的事了。后来的饭局中听说国庆他们一家国庆要回欧阳太<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"太湖\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10554.html\" target=\"_blank\">太湖</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>南<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"邵阳\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15540.html\" target=\"_blank\">邵阳</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"绥宁\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64487.html\" target=\"_blank\">绥宁</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>的老家，恬不知耻的我数次提出同往一游，可能是酒精的麻痹，也可能是严重低估了我的死皮赖脸，最后无奈的答应，幸福是要争取的，风雅是要附庸的，我心里不禁为自己一阵鼓掌！不过当时看着欧阳先生生无可恋的样子，心想他脑海中的画面应该是多年前的经典电视剧中唐国强坐在木椅，摇着羽扇，而画外音则是：我从未见过有如此厚颜无耻之人！</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879471561.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/31/88/CoUBGV2j5BCAM1L6AAOy3sQcWgM642.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/31/88/CoUBGV2j5BCAM1L6AAOy3sQcWgM642.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/31/88/CoUBGV2j5BCAM1L6AAOy3sQcWgM642.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879471561\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"879471563\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">十月一日开了将近十八个小时才到<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64487.html\" data-kw=\"绥宁\" target=\"_blank\">绥宁</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，这不是我这些年国庆旅行中最长的时间，所以不觉得有什么问题，肥妻好像也没什么过激反应，其实当假期高速公路堵车成为一种常态，习惯了便会处之泰然，一如苦涩的咖啡和茶；臭飘万里的臭豆腐；边吃边流汗流泪流鼻涕的辛辣菜式，不一样受到万千宠爱，每天必喝，隔天要尝吗？除了人类受虐倾向严重之外，更主要的是苦涩辛辣过后的回甘，为了得到一瞬的快感，忍受种种痛苦又算什么呢？</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879471921.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/25/wKgEaV2j5DyANMvTAAU7mSBhD0w833.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/25/wKgEaV2j5DyANMvTAAU7mSBhD0w833.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/25/wKgEaV2j5DyANMvTAAU7mSBhD0w833.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879471921\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"879471923\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">乡村的早晨都会自然醒，因为到时候就会有主旋律响起，这主旋律不是我们普通认知的那种，而是乡村特有的鸡鸣鸭叫犬吠，你不醒也得醒！我倒是没什么问题，虽然两点才睡，一把年纪睡不多，但红颜和挚友就不太习惯了，是的，他们也跟着来了，似乎第一段末尾唐国强的经典台词更适合他们。吃过早饭，真的是吃饭，比早餐迟，比午饭早，不过农家饭菜于城市人来说异常美味，美食有时更像仙丹灵药，不止能解决饥饿，还能消除疲劳，精神饱满的我们向第一站宝鼎山出发！</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473003.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/8A/CoUBGV2j5LaAYbLbAAuY55-ZVYs172.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/8A/CoUBGV2j5LaAYbLbAAuY55-ZVYs172.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/8A/CoUBGV2j5LaAYbLbAAuY55-ZVYs172.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473003\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473004.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/97/CoUBGV2j5LuAVeskAA-s93B59FE108.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/97/CoUBGV2j5LuAVeskAA-s93B59FE108.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/97/CoUBGV2j5LuAVeskAA-s93B59FE108.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473004\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473005.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/E6/wKgEaV2j5L6AB_9dAAmKo5RYkPY982.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/E6/wKgEaV2j5L6AB_9dAAmKo5RYkPY982.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/E6/wKgEaV2j5L6AB_9dAAmKo5RYkPY982.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473005\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473006.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/ED/wKgEaV2j5MCAYiY6AAuEVTNIHuY954.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/ED/wKgEaV2j5MCAYiY6AAuEVTNIHuY954.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/ED/wKgEaV2j5MCAYiY6AAuEVTNIHuY954.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473006\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473007.html\"><img src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/F6/wKgEaV2j5MSAD_ZKAA1SkEedRW4994.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/F6/wKgEaV2j5MSAD_ZKAA1SkEedRW4994.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A8/F6/wKgEaV2j5MSAD_ZKAA1SkEedRW4994.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473007\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473008.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/B1/CoUBGV2j5MaAdSOhAAdRZG-5S8U767.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/B1/CoUBGV2j5MaAdSOhAAdRZG-5S8U767.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/B1/CoUBGV2j5MaAdSOhAAdRZG-5S8U767.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473008\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473009.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/B5/CoUBGV2j5MiAA0s3AAVAW8H4bPA715.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/B5/CoUBGV2j5MiAA0s3AAVAW8H4bPA715.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/B5/CoUBGV2j5MiAA0s3AAVAW8H4bPA715.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473009\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473010.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/BA/CoUBGV2j5MqAAaRKAAc6QG3SwYg845.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/BA/CoUBGV2j5MqAAaRKAAc6QG3SwYg845.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/32/BA/CoUBGV2j5MqAAaRKAAc6QG3SwYg845.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473010\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/64487/scenery_17337889/879473093.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A9/40/wKgEaV2j5OCAESslAAx-sAaisX8587.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A9/40/wKgEaV2j5OCAESslAAx-sAaisX8587.jpg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A9/40/wKgEaV2j5OCAESslAAx-sAaisX8587.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"879473093\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"879473019\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><br>宝鼎山不高，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145805.html\" data-kw=\"大树\" target=\"_blank\">大树</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>也不多，只有一些灌木，不过花草茂盛一片绿色的山丘起伏，山顶上一个个巨大的风车参差排列，驱车上山，沿路风景也算怡人。车将近到山顶就走不动了，路还没完全修好，我们只好徒步登顶。山顶处有一座半城堡式的石头房子，走近一看，原来是座寺庙，归元寺名字大气，但庙宇简陋，虽说始建于元朝，清朝重修，可惜山和庙都不出名，所以也只能勉强维持，寺庙布局基本合格，我问寺里唯一的老和尚这里属于哪一派别，老和尚竟然答不出来，只说是自己看经书修行的，原来是一散修，没有大宗门支持，怪不得如此落魄。知道欧阳一家对佛教没什么了解，我特别高兴，于是从寺庙布局，到韦驮姿势，再到三世佛、三身佛、三方佛一顿胡吹乱侃，看到他们听完后一脸如坠雾里的样子，我更是洋洋自得，从归元寺出来时，赵老师说我讲解时，那老和尚几次想插口都插不进来，急的额头冒汗，样子十分好笑，我听后霎时觉得全身毛孔都张开了，像是喝了仙露甘泉让人神清气爽，舒服得不要不要的。</p>', '6', '特别策划', '1', '2022-06-08', '10', '1000', '一个人', '2022-06-05 17:11:43');
INSERT INTO `diary` VALUES ('4', '时至2017年12月下旬儿子年假还没歇，与我们商议全家出游，提议自驾漠河 ，因恐道路冰雪被我们', '自驾漠河', '安徽', 'http://localhost:8081/image/diary/4/4.webp', '<p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot; Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\" data-fr-verified=\"true\">20天我们穿越了加利福尼亚州，犹他州，亚利桑那州，怀俄明州，蒙大拿州，爱达荷州，&nbsp;内华达州共七个州。<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">老天实在是很偏爱美洲，不仅给了它海洋、高山，还给了它鬼斧神工的峡谷、拱门，以及惊人的黄石公园。<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">一路上的美景各有特色，黄石国家公园是世界上最壮观的国家公园之一；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">哈瓦苏湖城的伦敦桥是目前世界上最大的移建建筑物；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">科罗拉多大峡谷是世界上最大的峡谷之一，也是地球上自然界七大奇景之一；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Pfeiffer&nbsp;Beach海滩是世界七大彩色海滩之一；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">羚羊谷是世上最怪异的20大旅游去处之一；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">国家拱门公园是世界上最大的自然沙岩拱门集中地；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">摩门圣殿是盐湖城的标志，也是全世界摩门教徒的圣地；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">了解了阿甘之路奔跑的意义：<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">你得丢开以往的事，才能不断继续前进；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">布莱斯峡谷，其内的红色、橙色与白色的岩石形成了奇特的自然景观，被誉为天然石俑的殿堂，由于海拔较高，是我们此次旅行最冷的地方，鸭绒衣，披肩都裹身上还是冷 ；<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">色彩艳丽的峡谷是锡安国家公园的写照。<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在黄石公园看到了麋鹿，野牛，熊，狼……&nbsp;<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;美景可以看下面照片领略一二<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">6月5号下午3点从焦作坐机场大巴到新郑机场。<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">久违的雨今天突然倾盆而下，晚上21：<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">05的飞机被通知延误到次日00：<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">30，这样我们1：<br style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">20飞洛杉矶的航班也赶不上了，这次旅行行程安排都被打乱了。</span>\r\n\r\n<br></p>', '9', '特别策划', '1', '2022-06-02', '10', '1000', '家庭出游', '2022-06-05 17:09:57');
INSERT INTO `diary` VALUES ('5', '薄荷味儿的薄荷岛，陆地出海玩法全攻略！', '薄荷味儿的薄荷岛，陆地出海玩法全攻略！', '安徽', 'http://localhost:8081/image/diary/5/5.webp', '<h2>你不知道的薄荷岛</h2><p>\r\n\r\n如果你跟没去之前的我一样，对薄荷岛一无所知，那么这段我呕心沥血的科普，请仔细看完。毕竟我也是边听导游讲解边拿小本本记下的。</p><p>首先，给你们看我自己的简易手绘版地图，像不像一只海龟~\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/22/BD/wKgBZ1o3Y3iAYa-4AAgeHWrOnuI42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/22/BD/wKgBZ1o3Y3iAYa-4AAgeHWrOnuI42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/22/BD/wKgBZ1o3Y3iAYa-4AAgeHWrOnuI42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">\r\n\r\n整个薄荷岛由薄荷本岛、邦劳岛以及周边无数个小岛组成，其中月牙形的处女岛以及浮潜必去的巴里卡萨岛都是围绕着薄荷本岛周边的小岛。而邦劳岛则是大部分游客会选择留宿的地方，我们这次也是住在邦劳岛的度假村。特别要说的是邦劳岛上的alona海滩，算是整个薄荷岛的市中心，有很多的大排档，各种商店，各种浮潜店都聚集在这里，大部分的跳岛游行程，也是从alona海滩出发。而一些陆地景点，巧克力山及眼镜猴植物园都在薄荷本岛上。\r\n\r\n</p><h2>薄荷岛陆地游——会魔法是我的秘密</h2><h3>像哈利波特飞跃巧克力山</h3><p>\r\n\r\n巧克力山(Chocolate&nbsp;Hills)可以说是薄荷岛上最著名的景点，1268座圆锥形的小山横亘在土地上，壮观雄伟。每年五月份时这些小山就变成灰褐色，想象力丰富的菲律宾人便把这里称作巧克力山。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/28/BF/wKgBZ1ovT_SAJWqxAAgzZ0ODt-w07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/28/BF/wKgBZ1ovT_SAJWqxAAgzZ0ODt-w07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/28/BF/wKgBZ1ovT_SAJWqxAAgzZ0ODt-w07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">巧克力山\r\n\r\n巧克力山位于薄荷岛的中部，《哈利·波特》曾在此取景，去山顶租一把“魔法帚”，魔法之旅从此处开始。遗憾的是，我并没有找到凹造型的扫把~</p><p>巧克力山的颜色四季变化，唯有旱季来此，山顶的草被晒成棕黄色，才会呈现出如名所唤的咖啡色景象。我们去的时候草还是绿的，谁说不可以是抹茶巧克力！\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/27/F2/wKgBZ1ovT2OAPIkEAAIRH4h_Ppc52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/27/F2/wKgBZ1ovT2OAPIkEAAIRH4h_Ppc52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/27/F2/wKgBZ1ovT2OAPIkEAAIRH4h_Ppc52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">巧克力山\r\n\r\n我们去参观的那天，有点阴天，还下了会儿雨。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/37/2A/wKgBZ1o3cXGAJyV5ACYCC4TaQFA30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/37/2A/wKgBZ1o3cXGAJyV5ACYCC4TaQFA30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/37/2A/wKgBZ1o3cXGAJyV5ACYCC4TaQFA30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">我心爱的小伙伴、miki和我<b>Tips：</b></p><p>这里有个空中自行车的项目，因为那时下雨，我就没有去玩，如果你们之后去天气好的话去体验一下哦！\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=3&amp;amp;id=5472831&amp;amp;poi_type_id=3\" target=\"_blank\" data-title=\"巧克力山\" data-id=\"5472831\" data-type=\"2\">\r\n  <img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/C2/77/wKgBEFtWfm6AbE8-AAT5a57pR2045.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21240x240r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21240x240%2Fquality%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">\r\n\r\n  <h2>巧克力山</h2>\r\n\r\n    <p>巧克力山位于薄荷岛的中部，共有1268座。它的形成颇具神话色彩。传说古时有两个巨人用石头向对方互相投掷，巨石一个一个掉在地上，便形成了数以千计，造型优美的圆锥型山头。其中两座山头已发展成为渡假胜地，住宿、餐饮、观景、娱乐设施业已完备。这些山曾有过别的名字，直到有一个英国教师来到这里，看到旱季的小山上因为草被晒成了棕黄色，而形状又很像国外的一种巧克力，因而命名为巧克力。这些巧克力山上长满了植被，主要是当地的一种茅草、野生甘蔗、菊花和一些蕨类植物。这些植物的颜色随季节、气温、雨量变化而改变：春天嫩绿、夏天深绿、初秋蛋黄、深秋黄红，旱季则变成棕褐的咖啡色。</p>\r\n</a></p><h3>和眼镜猴比谁的眼睛大</h3><p>\r\n\r\n攀附在树枝上睡觉的小小眼镜猴，乍一看，还以为是正在养精蓄锐的蝙蝠。在眼镜猴保护区，这个体型小，眼睛大又圆的菲律宾国宝，仿佛大自然施展魔法的小精灵，可爱灵动至极。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2B/EB/wKgBZ1ovUiaAF_iNAAIU8WVNmwg61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2B/EB/wKgBZ1ovUiaAF_iNAAIU8WVNmwg61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2B/EB/wKgBZ1ovUiaAF_iNAAIU8WVNmwg61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">唯一一只睁眼的眼睛猴\r\n\r\n白天眼镜猴要补觉，只有几只被工作人员抓出来供游客参观。我大概看了有5、6只都是双眼紧闭甜甜的睡着，但一心想着要和眼镜猴比眼睛大的我不能放弃，终于等到一只睁眼的，抓紧拍了张照片，它就又睡了，所以至今到底谁的眼睛更大这件事，请待下回一争高下。\r\n\r\n<b>Tips：</b></p><p>眼镜猴保护区可以拍照，切记不可开闪光灯，闪光灯会伤害眼镜猴脆弱的眼睛。还有一点就是，动静要小，人家在睡觉啦。\r\n\r\n</p><h3>罗博河漂流午餐——妹纸辣么美，唱歌辣么棒</h3><p>\r\n\r\n罗博河(Loboc&nbsp;River)是唯一一条流经薄荷岛的淡水河，也被誉为“东方的亚马逊河”。泛舟巡游是游览罗博河最好的方式，船上提供自助餐，边吃边欣赏着两岸原始的热带雨林风光和神秘的丛林动物，还有当地歌手live演唱会，穿着草裙舞的土著居民还会在岸上表演，令人感到无比惬意。</p><p>巡河游览门票：550比索\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8A/18/wKgBZ1owppiAC5rkAAmEenf7BwA722.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8A/18/wKgBZ1owppiAC5rkAAmEenf7BwA722.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8A/18/wKgBZ1owppiAC5rkAAmEenf7BwA722.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">罗博河游船<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8A/24/wKgBZ1owpqeAS44MAAwFGmzbjvA196.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8A/24/wKgBZ1owpqeAS44MAAwFGmzbjvA196.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8A/24/wKgBZ1owpqeAS44MAAwFGmzbjvA196.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">游船上的自助餐\r\n\r\n不要问我饭好不好吃，因为从头到尾我只做了一件事，就是直勾勾的盯着船上唱歌的妹纸！怎么辣么美呀犯规犯规！嗓音也超级棒，那首《noting&nbsp;gonna&nbsp;change&nbsp;my&nbsp;love&nbsp;for&nbsp;you》真的分分钟掰弯我的节奏！紧张到不敢搭讪也不敢要合照的迷妹就是我啦！感谢同行小伙伴的皂片和视频哦！\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8C/3C/wKgBZ1owqPuACOyeAALOjLrs-7Y49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8C/3C/wKgBZ1owqPuACOyeAALOjLrs-7Y49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8C/3C/wKgBZ1owqPuACOyeAALOjLrs-7Y49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">这就是我爱的妹纸，感谢孙哥供图</p><h3>做一次虔诚的信徒可好——巴卡来运大教堂</h3><p>\r\n\r\n菲律宾是天主教国家，相对原生态的薄荷岛同样拥有相当数量的教堂，其中，巴卡来运大教堂是最古老的一座。这个教堂坐落在乡村小路边，是西班牙殖民时期建立的第一座教堂，大概有420年历史，外表古老沧桑，但内部金碧辉煌，庄严神圣。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1F/80/wKgBZ1o3X9WAMGPdAAMQUOq0H-o57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1F/80/wKgBZ1o3X9WAMGPdAAMQUOq0H-o57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/1F/80/wKgBZ1o3X9WAMGPdAAMQUOq0H-o57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">巴卡来运大教堂 图片来自网络\r\n\r\n因为前两年的大地震，这座教堂毁损严重，一直在施工维护，内部谢绝参观，我们只能在外围走一走，感受它古老的气韵。它的外观其貌不扬，但却有着奇特的建筑经历——它是由珊瑚和石头为主要原材料筑建的，而黏和剂是沙子、石灰石和蛋清的混合物。墙壁上的黑色印记、石板上的绿色苔藓、油漆脱落大半的木门，无不见证着时光荏苒。\r\n\r\n<b>Tips：</b></p><p>穿着短袖短裤是不允许进入教堂的，请尊重当地文化，注意自己的着装。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=3&amp;amp;id=6318678&amp;amp;poi_type_id=3\" target=\"_blank\" data-title=\"巴克雷扬教堂\" data-id=\"6318678\" data-type=\"2\">\r\n  <img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/8E/wKgBEFsnkhyASIGOAA_jYUIGyEo33.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21240x240r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21240x240%2Fquality%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">\r\n\r\n  <h2>巴克雷扬教堂</h2>\r\n\r\n    <p>巴克雷扬教堂是菲律宾最古老的教堂，建于420多年前，至今保存完好。这座建筑外观看来其貌不扬，但却有着奇特的建筑经历——它是由珊瑚和石头为主要原材料筑建的，而黏和剂是沙子、石灰石和蛋清的混合物。教堂内还有一座博物馆，收藏了不少宗教遗物，包括用金线编制的法衣，写在羊皮上的拉丁文教堂音乐歌词等。该教堂以奇特的天花板壁画和雕工复杂的古忏悔室为荣，选择一个阳光充沛的时间进入，地上会映射出美丽的彩色琉璃光影，很有韵味。</p>\r\n</a></p><h3>我们热爱和平——歃血为盟纪念碑</h3><p>\r\n\r\n血盟公园是菲律宾人与西班牙殖民者间友好交往的标志性建筑，在这里可以看到许多反映当地人民与西班牙人间深厚友谊的雕塑。当地首领与西班牙登陆者歃血为盟，将鲜血滴入葡萄酒中，从而结下了深厚的情谊。值得一提的是，这里面朝大海，景色怡人，也是观赏海景的绝佳地点。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/83/CF/wKgBZ1owoB2AMCk0AA-j0-FRIjc50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/83/CF/wKgBZ1owoB2AMCk0AA-j0-FRIjc50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/83/CF/wKgBZ1owoB2AMCk0AA-j0-FRIjc50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">歃血为盟纪念碑<a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=3&amp;amp;id=6318696&amp;amp;poi_type_id=3\" target=\"_blank\" data-title=\"血盟纪念碑\" data-id=\"6318696\" data-type=\"2\">\r\n  <img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s3/M00/16/24/wKgBt0-NYBSqB461AAPrHMhn-ts53.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21240x240r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21240x240%2Fquality%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">\r\n\r\n  <h2>血盟纪念碑</h2>\r\n\r\n    <p>血盟纪念碑铜像位于塔比拉兰市中心，为游客呈现一段两国结盟历史。 所谓的纪念碑，並不只有一块碑坊，而是一群雕刻生动的雕像。雕像描述西方人与菲律宾认围坐，共同举杯，歃血为盟，以示友好，代表菲律宾与西方国家订定的第一个友好条约，具有极重大的历史意义。铁灰色的铜像，庄严的表情，象征菲律宾在国际地位上变化的历史痕迹。</p>\r\n</a></p><h2>没吃过鲜花，怎敢称小仙女</h2><p>\r\n\r\n蜂蜜农场位于邦劳岛东海岸的悬崖边上，是一家集花卉蔬菜培育、蜂蜜采集制作、餐饮和客房经营为一体的综合农场，占地很广。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/89/7A/wKgBZ1ovmImACRzJAARKijRN-FU73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/89/7A/wKgBZ1ovmImACRzJAARKijRN-FU73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/89/7A/wKgBZ1ovmImACRzJAARKijRN-FU73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">蜜蜂农场\r\n\r\n花瓣沙拉、蜂蜜面包、蜂蜜冰淇淋等等都是这个农场的特色美食，这些食物既愉悦眼球又养颜美容。大名鼎鼎的<b>鲜花沙拉</b>，整盘都是由各种各样可食用的花瓣混合而成，独特且爽口。如果你没吃过花，不妨试试看；如果吃过，蜂蜜农场的花更美味哦。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8B/C7/wKgBZ1ovmmmAO2TsAAx5MNhhUHU45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8B/C7/wKgBZ1ovmmmAO2TsAAx5MNhhUHU45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8B/C7/wKgBZ1ovmmmAO2TsAAx5MNhhUHU45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">鲜花沙拉\r\n\r\n蜜蜂农场是我们那天陆地游的最后一站，也是我最喜欢的一站，可是那天我们晚餐另有安排，只是参观一下就走了。但是！蜜蜂农场的鲜花沙拉，是我在来之前立下的flag！一进农场就直奔餐厅，点了鲜花有机沙拉，有辣的和酸甜的酱汁可选。吃下一整个鲜花，瞬间觉得自己变美了不少！\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8C/A4/wKgBZ1ovmyCATFdoACT7zTlPUwg37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8C/A4/wKgBZ1ovmyCATFdoACT7zTlPUwg37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8C/A4/wKgBZ1ovmyCATFdoACT7zTlPUwg37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">认真吃鲜花的小仙女没错啦\r\n\r\n蜜蜂农场的手工冰激凌是和鲜花沙拉齐名的必吃哦！有多种味道可以选。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/08/BF/wKgBZ1o3RkCAXjqDAAzyJ-ALQQ040.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/08/BF/wKgBZ1o3RkCAXjqDAAzyJ-ALQQ040.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/08/BF/wKgBZ1o3RkCAXjqDAAzyJ-ALQQ040.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">认真吃冰激凌的孙哥\r\n\r\n其实它的名字叫蜜蜂农场，但不单纯是一个农场哦，同时还经营着餐厅，住宿和商店。他们家商店还有很多纪念品可以买，比如蜂蜜，手做面包，手工做的蜜蜂皂，木瓜皂，精油等等。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/20/3D/wKgBZ1o3YJ2Aead2AAUBfKwKr8Q162.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/20/3D/wKgBZ1o3YJ2Aead2AAUBfKwKr8Q162.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/20/3D/wKgBZ1o3YJ2Aead2AAUBfKwKr8Q162.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">蜜蜂农场商店的各种制品</p><h2>跳岛游——我们仙女都是喝露水长大的</h2><h3>海豚宝宝——你知道我在等你吗</h3><p>\r\n\r\n出海寻觅海豚是薄荷岛不容错过的体验项目之一。一般都是从alona海滩乘坐螃蟹船出海，你唯一要做的就是早起！但是能不能亲密接触海豚还是要看缘分，等到海豚在你眼前出现的一刻，会给人不期而遇的惊喜。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/66/EF/wKgBZ1ovgtCAYo7iAA21KLrtfzw41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/66/EF/wKgBZ1ovgtCAYo7iAA21KLrtfzw41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/66/EF/wKgBZ1ovgtCAYo7iAA21KLrtfzw41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">在甲板等海豚的我\r\n\r\n那天我们6点就出发了，估计海豚还在睡梦中。大概一小时之后，同行的船越来越少，估计好多都放弃了，我们还在坚持寻找。就在我准备进船去躲避阳光的时候，海豚出现了。软乎乎滑溜溜的在海里翻滚，真的是刚睡醒的慵懒样儿。&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><h3>巴里卡萨——大断层潜水</h3><p>\r\n\r\n看完海豚我们就去巴里卡萨潜水去啦！巴里卡萨岛离薄荷岛有45分钟航程。这里已被世界联合国组织列为保护的海底区域，是顶级的潜水天堂，景观相当壮丽。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/61/E0/wKgBZ1ovf2mAMn7SAAtl78xfETw27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/61/E0/wKgBZ1ovf2mAMn7SAAtl78xfETw27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/61/E0/wKgBZ1ovf2mAMn7SAAtl78xfETw27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">from温柔菲律宾旅游局miki\r\n\r\n这里的海水很清澈，可以直接看到海底的珊瑚群和斑斓的鱼群，非常适合潜水。来到薄荷岛，肯定要体验潜水，体验一下与鱼嬉戏，想象自己也变成海中一员，在波澜的水中翩翩起舞。巴里卡萨岛是位于海中央的一座珊瑚小岛，也是潜水胜地。在这附近的<b>大断层潜水一定特别enjoy啦！</b></p><p>下一次，等我能接受我能变黑的时候，我们再约！\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/62/D4/wKgBZ1ovgAKAaoMqAAWd7UzaNno91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/62/D4/wKgBZ1ovgAKAaoMqAAWd7UzaNno91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/62/D4/wKgBZ1ovgAKAaoMqAAWd7UzaNno91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">巴里卡萨的海底</p><h3>处女座的处女岛</h3><p>\r\n\r\n这座岛在早上和晚上时会被海水淹没，只有在中午至傍晚的退潮时分才可以看到美丽的月牙形海滩。翠绿的泻湖位于月牙形沙滩的中央，如同一颗蓝色宝石。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2D/71/wKgBZ1ovUySACOKvAAoP-mcAEek19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2D/71/wKgBZ1ovUySACOKvAAoP-mcAEek19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2D/71/wKgBZ1ovUySACOKvAAoP-mcAEek19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">处女岛\r\n\r\n都说处女岛现在商业化有点儿严重，但我觉得恰到好处！我们在这里吃到了此行最棒的海鲜——鲍鱼和海胆！还喝了新鲜的椰子！海鲜都是岛民就地取材，直接给你烤呀炒的！鲍鱼一定要吃烤的哦，特别肥美好吃到流泪；海胆应该就是很普通的煮了一下吧，放点醋也是很美味，更爱日本那种海胆的做法。</p><p>200p-300p就能吃到撑！\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/33/25/wKgBZ1ovVwaAQmLkAAe7wGhm1rs68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/33/25/wKgBZ1ovVwaAQmLkAAe7wGhm1rs68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/33/25/wKgBZ1ovVwaAQmLkAAe7wGhm1rs68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">海胆\r\n\r\n还有，只有在菲律宾才能吃到的炸香蕉！我的小伙伴都说好吃哒，可是对于我这种在日本连续多年吃菲律宾香蕉的人，原谅我实在下不了口~\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s6/M00/D5/BB/wKgB4lLwtY2AY5jBAAcHqbaw6gQ62.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s6/M00/D5/BB/wKgB4lLwtY2AY5jBAAcHqbaw6gQ62.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s6/M00/D5/BB/wKgB4lLwtY2AY5jBAAcHqbaw6gQ62.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">菲律宾当地美食炸香蕉<b>要特别提醒大家</b>，大部分的螃蟹船并不能直接停靠到处女岛，需要下船自己趟水过去，但是请相信我，一定要上岛，那么优质的白沙滩一定要去踩呀踩，关键拍照无敌美！即便你跟我一样，去的那天怕晒黑穿的是长裤，也一定要果断脱掉裤子，换上泳衣，趟水上岛。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/30/7B/wKgBZ1ovVN6AVotMAAZ-_W-7EEs13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/30/7B/wKgBZ1ovVN6AVotMAAZ-_W-7EEs13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/30/7B/wKgBZ1ovVN6AVotMAAZ-_W-7EEs13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">我有下水！\r\n\r\n这也成了我此次出海唯一湿身的地方，所以我坚信我是下水了的（有图为证）！尽管我的导游一直嘲笑我，来海岛国家你都没下水！\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2A/39/wKgBZ1o3aJOAJ3GCABCIYax-dVA54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2A/39/wKgBZ1o3aJOAJ3GCABCIYax-dVA54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/2A/39/wKgBZ1o3aJOAJ3GCABCIYax-dVA54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">我有下水之二！<a href=\"https://m.mafengwo.cn/nb/public/sharejump.php?type=3&amp;amp;id=5472858&amp;amp;poi_type_id=3\" target=\"_blank\" data-title=\"处女岛\" data-id=\"5472858\" data-type=\"2\">\r\n  <img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/EB/2B/wKgBs1Z2OsWATH4OAAU5RVgbVek12.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21240x240r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21240x240%2Fquality%2F90\" class=\"fr-fin\">\r\n\r\n  <h2>处女岛</h2>\r\n\r\n    <p>处女岛真名为Pontod Island，是一个无人小岛，隐藏在冰蓝色薄荷海之中的小岛有着两道美丽的半月形环带沙滩，中间围绕着翠绿的泻湖。这样的生态环境养育了。一般船家会在上午和中午退潮时候带领游客登录这个小岛，那时有许多售卖海胆的当地人蜂拥而至，争相兜售新鲜打捞出来的海鲜，只要10-15比索你就能大饱口福啦。</p>\r\n</a></p><h2>两天玩转薄荷岛</h2><p>\r\n\r\n以上，两天的行程基本就玩遍了薄荷岛，个人觉得也是既轻松又充实的安排。无论你是自由行，还是跟团游，都很推荐这样玩。</p><p><b>总结：薄荷岛两日玩法攻略</b></p>', '2', '特别策划', '1', '2022-06-08', '10', '1000', '一个人', '2022-06-05 16:56:08');
INSERT INTO `diary` VALUES ('6', '10月国庆格聂南线穿越行记', '作为 中国 7大顶级越野线路之一， 格聂 南线蕴藏着极致诱惑的原始美景: 雪山、', '安徽', 'http://localhost:8081/image/diary/6/6.webp', '<p data-seq=\"874043092\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">作为<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"中国\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>7大顶级越野线路之一，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a data-kw=\"格聂\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>南线蕴藏着极致诱惑的原始美景: 雪山、冰川、草甸、森林、海子、溪流、温泉、峡谷、藏寨、牛羊......还有淳朴的民风。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889249406.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/84/C4/CoUBGV2p7ImAf1NGAA3skTzCAGg63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/84/C4/CoUBGV2p7ImAf1NGAA3skTzCAGg63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/84/C4/CoUBGV2p7ImAf1NGAA3skTzCAGg63.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889249406\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6005625.html\" data-poiid=\"6005625\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">冷古寺</a></p><p data-seq=\"889249408\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">随着<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>神山管理筹备组的成立，“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>南线”将与“丙察察”一样，成为越野里最后的“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>南线”这一说法又日渐喧嚣尘上。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889275889.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/B0/5C/CoUBGV2qewWACxMKAB8kGuXTgj461.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/B0/5C/CoUBGV2qewWACxMKAB8kGuXTgj461.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/B0/5C/CoUBGV2qewWACxMKAB8kGuXTgj461.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889275889\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6005625.html\" data-poiid=\"6005625\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">冷古寺</a></p><p data-seq=\"889275897\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">为了赶在景区完全开发前一饱眼福，我和鱼两人开着小吉踏上了穿越<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>南线的旅程，走咧，去高原上撒欢。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889239365.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/8C/28/CoUBGV2qcCCAJOa1ABDU9Cyx1As95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/8C/28/CoUBGV2qcCCAJOa1ABDU9Cyx1As95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/8C/28/CoUBGV2qcCCAJOa1ABDU9Cyx1As95.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889239365\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6706453.html\" data-poiid=\"6706453\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">铁匠山垭口</a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6005625.html\">冷古寺</a></p><p data-seq=\"889239370\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">出发前准备<br>一、基本情况</p><p data-seq=\"885377306\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>神山: 位于<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12703.html\" data-kw=\"四川\" target=\"_blank\">四川</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>省<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10236.html\" data-kw=\"甘孜\" target=\"_blank\">甘孜</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>州<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10509.html\" data-kw=\"理塘\" target=\"_blank\">理塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县西南部、<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11719.html\" data-kw=\"巴塘\" target=\"_blank\">巴塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县东部。藏语名为呷玛日巴，是我国藏传佛教24座神山中的第13女神，也是胜乐金刚的八大金刚妙语圣地之一。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889157200.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/66/68/CoUBGV2qZJiAFruJAA4KVgv9Er805.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/66/68/CoUBGV2qZJiAFruJAA4KVgv9Er805.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/66/68/CoUBGV2qZJiAFruJAA4KVgv9Er805.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889157200\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/74288916.html\" data-poiid=\"74288916\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">格聂之眼</a></p><p data-seq=\"889157204\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>山区群峰林立，5000米以上的高峰多达数十座。山顶终年积雪，坡壁峥嵘陡峭，山麓一片片高原森林，下面的草甸构成辽阔的高原牧场。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889157716.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/69/53/CoUBGV2qZaOABJkLABFcXqMHcig57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/69/53/CoUBGV2qZaOABJkLABFcXqMHcig57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/69/53/CoUBGV2qZaOABJkLABFcXqMHcig57.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889157716\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"889157666\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">其中尤推海拔5807米的肖扎神山、海拔5780米的克麦隆神山，和海拔6204米的<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>主峰最受尊崇，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>主峰号称<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12703.html\" data-kw=\"四川\" target=\"_blank\">四川</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>第三高峰、康区第一高峰。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/885378363.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/DF/10/CoUBGV2nU3qAdwNmABX8RDiyPVo34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/DF/10/CoUBGV2nU3qAdwNmABX8RDiyPVo34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/DF/10/CoUBGV2nU3qAdwNmABX8RDiyPVo34.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"885378363\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6414754.html\" data-poiid=\"6414754\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">格聂神山</a></p><p data-seq=\"885378365\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>南线: 是从<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10509.html\" data-kw=\"理塘\" target=\"_blank\">理塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县出发，沿着<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>神山的南侧穿行，终点到<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11719.html\" data-kw=\"巴塘\" target=\"_blank\">巴塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县的一条线路，全长230公里，行程约1~2天。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889250632.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/98/29/CoUBGV2qc-6AVnFbABNxMLjDzmk31.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/98/29/CoUBGV2qc-6AVnFbABNxMLjDzmk31.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/98/29/CoUBGV2qc-6AVnFbABNxMLjDzmk31.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889250632\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15409.html\" data-poiid=\"15409\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">理塘草原</a></p><p data-seq=\"889250636\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这条线路全程在平均海拔4000米以上的高原行驶，全线几乎没有手机信号，仅在路过为数不多的几个乡村时，车外有缥缈的信号渗进来，立马一把抓住发个圈，证明我还好好的。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889246512.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/92/4E/CoUBGV2qcf-ARnGlAA06O9DAb3A03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/92/4E/CoUBGV2qcf-ARnGlAA06O9DAb3A03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/92/4E/CoUBGV2qcf-ARnGlAA06O9DAb3A03.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889246512\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"889246526\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">路况：冷达之前的90公里是铺装路面，其余是简易的碎石路、土路、悬崖路，路面凹凸布满炮弹坑。坡陡弯急，路窄时会车困难；全程无加油站，一定要在<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10509.html\" data-kw=\"理塘\" target=\"_blank\">理塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>加满油后再行进，加油时要提供行驶证、驾驶证、身份证以供查验；沿途几乎没有路牌，找路全靠问，多与往来车辆交流路况及路线，避免走错路；与藏族同胞沟通有障碍时，连说带划的肢体语言是最好的交流工具。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889240169.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/8D/22/CoUBGV2qcGaAO2swAAvk5acKaHA51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/8D/22/CoUBGV2qcGaAO2swAAvk5acKaHA51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/8D/22/CoUBGV2qcGaAO2swAAvk5acKaHA51.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889240169\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6414814.html\" data-poiid=\"6414814\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">毛垭大草原</a></p><p data-seq=\"889240173\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11719.html\" data-kw=\"巴塘\" target=\"_blank\">巴塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县城，听当地老司机说，三年以后这条路的路面改造将会完成，届时轿车穿行应该也不成问题。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889157442.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/67/A7/CoUBGV2qZQSAZJfCAAeQQdkDA2c32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/67/A7/CoUBGV2qZQSAZJfCAAeQQdkDA2c32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/67/A7/CoUBGV2qZQSAZJfCAAeQQdkDA2c32.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889157442\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"889157444\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">马年是<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>的本命年，届时会有很多朝圣者从各地前往<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>转山。<br><br>二、关注了微信公众号“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>神山旅游”和“<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10236.html\" data-kw=\"甘孜\" target=\"_blank\">甘孜</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>交警”，查询到<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>神山管理处电话：0836-5324111、<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10236.html\" data-kw=\"甘孜\" target=\"_blank\">甘孜</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>州公安局交通警察支队的咨询电话0836-2822963，随时关注实时问询，以便第一时间了解到天气变化和最新路况，避免错过因故封路的即时信息。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889252232.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9A/EE/CoUBGV2qdNWAat07ABmyLkZ2dQA25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9A/EE/CoUBGV2qdNWAat07ABmyLkZ2dQA25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9A/EE/CoUBGV2qdNWAat07ABmyLkZ2dQA25.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889252232\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/2434672.html\" data-poiid=\"2434672\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">剪子弯山</a></p><p data-seq=\"889252246\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">根据<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>神山的公众号内容推荐，大致确定了行程线路：<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10509.html\" data-kw=\"理塘\" target=\"_blank\">理塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县城—铁匠山—喇嘛垭乡—依<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/147435.html\" data-kw=\"拉卡\" target=\"_blank\">拉卡</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>垭口—热日卡露天温泉—乃干拉托<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>之眼—乃干多村—冷达—虎皮坝—冷古寺—热梯河谷—格木村—<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11719.html\" data-kw=\"巴塘\" target=\"_blank\">巴塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县城。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889252482.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9B/F5/CoUBGV2qdR-AIMFTABko4a1W5PM42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9B/F5/CoUBGV2qdR-AIMFTABko4a1W5PM42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9B/F5/CoUBGV2qdR-AIMFTABko4a1W5PM42.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889252482\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6414754.html\" data-poiid=\"6414754\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">格聂神山</a></p><p data-seq=\"889252484\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">三、行李准备: 打印出的行李清单，逐一对照勾选，准备行李，再备些简单的文具和小食品用于分享给穿越途中遇到的小朋友。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/885256520.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/92/F3/CoUBGV2m_IqAbCB4AABovJTYcVc603.PNG?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/92/F3/CoUBGV2m_IqAbCB4AABovJTYcVc603.PNG?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/92/F3/CoUBGV2m_IqAbCB4AABovJTYcVc603.PNG?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"885256520\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"885256522\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">四、了解目的地的民族禁忌，相互尊重，切勿犯忌。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889158669.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/6F/23/CoUBGV2qZ5OAD3ZkABRynFIluSU58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/6F/23/CoUBGV2qZ5OAD3ZkABRynFIluSU58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/6F/23/CoUBGV2qZ5OAD3ZkABRynFIluSU58.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889158669\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6414814.html\" data-poiid=\"6414814\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">毛垭大草原</a></p><p data-seq=\"889158673\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">准备就绪，接下来就开启穿越<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>之旅。<br>D1：<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" data-kw=\"重庆\" target=\"_blank\">重庆</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>-<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>-<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14727.html\" data-kw=\"新都桥\" target=\"_blank\">新都桥</a><br>10月2日，8:30分从<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" data-kw=\"重庆\" target=\"_blank\">重庆</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>出发，打算当晚宿<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，先逐步适应一下高海拔，待次日凌晨起早翻山，避免与大部队打拥堂。奈何计划没有变化快，我从<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15128.html\" data-kw=\"眉山\" target=\"_blank\">眉山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>服务区接手开车，一路行至<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，拥堵并不厉害。原计划16:00点左右到<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，结果在雅康高速<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>方向下道前缓行了一段路后，于17:00点过抵达<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>城区。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889158492.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/6E/5F/CoUBGV2qZ1KAcH3hAA6wKuJhjpk47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/6E/5F/CoUBGV2qZ1KAcH3hAA6wKuJhjpk47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/6E/5F/CoUBGV2qZ1KAcH3hAA6wKuJhjpk47.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889158492\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a></p><p data-seq=\"889158494\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">见时辰还早，从执勤交警处得知，折多山上未下雪、道路畅通，为免夜长梦多，当即决定连夜翻山（我们2018年国庆前往<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10011.html\" data-kw=\"色达\" target=\"_blank\">色达</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>途中，住在<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>的当晚即遇上下雪降温，折多山上，第二天即发生了为期数日的大堵车）。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889135926.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C4/B2/CoUBGV2qDxGAbubnAAuYkzcxK5413.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C4/B2/CoUBGV2qDxGAbubnAAuYkzcxK5413.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C4/B2/CoUBGV2qDxGAbubnAAuYkzcxK5413.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889135926\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a></p><p data-seq=\"889135928\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>城区内的道路弯弯绕绕，有点窄，上山后的路，换成老司机鱼来驾驶。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889136020.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C6/3E/CoUBGV2qECSAYt0KAA3viJTF34Y64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C6/3E/CoUBGV2qECSAYt0KAA3viJTF34Y64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C6/3E/CoUBGV2qECSAYt0KAA3viJTF34Y64.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889136020\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/2549166.html\" data-poiid=\"2549166\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">康定县</a></p><p data-seq=\"889136022\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在缓行的情况下，走了约1小时才逐步畅通。翻越折多山的过程中，天色渐黑，迷雾渐浓，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17257.html\" data-kw=\"盘山\" target=\"_blank\">盘山</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>公路折叠往返，一路上经过了有好几个超大观景平台。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/886998024.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/58/E4/CoUBGV2on5GAE6dIABFNrO8iMSY91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/58/E4/CoUBGV2on5GAE6dIABFNrO8iMSY91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/58/E4/CoUBGV2on5GAE6dIABFNrO8iMSY91.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"886998024\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/34899724.html\" data-poiid=\"34899724\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">折多山观雪台</a></p><p data-seq=\"886998034\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">有人已迫不及待停车休息，虽然这里天寒地冻，依旧抵挡不住游客们搭帐篷露营的热情。下山路上，经过<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10510.html\" data-kw=\"康定\" target=\"_blank\">康定</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>机场岔路口的时候，前方开始了新一轮的堵车。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889135818.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C3/83/CoUBGV2qDkSAYaKuABUm64kgJRI22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C3/83/CoUBGV2qDkSAYaKuABUm64kgJRI22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/C3/83/CoUBGV2qDkSAYaKuABUm64kgJRI22.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889135818\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15408.html\" data-poiid=\"15408\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">折多山</a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15408.html\">折多山</a></p><p data-seq=\"889135820\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">此刻，时针已指向19:00点，在山上被厚厚的云层遮掩得漆黑的天空，到这里却浓雾消散，洞现出绚丽的晚霞。烦躁的心情也随之烟消云散，开开心心堵过木雅圣地，驶往<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14727.html\" data-kw=\"新都桥\" target=\"_blank\">新都桥</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889253742.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/A1/5A/CoUBGV2qdrmAXJSZAA8OrOXk7yg79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/A1/5A/CoUBGV2qdrmAXJSZAA8OrOXk7yg79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/A1/5A/CoUBGV2qdrmAXJSZAA8OrOXk7yg79.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889253742\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6018060.html\" data-poiid=\"6018060\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">新都桥</a></p><p data-seq=\"889253767\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">记忆中，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14727.html\" data-kw=\"新都桥\" target=\"_blank\">新都桥</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>的国庆，必定是个找住宿异常困难的地方。商家坐地起价，到晚了，即使揣着银子也未必能找到栖身之所。然而，今天的<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14727.html\" data-kw=\"新都桥\" target=\"_blank\">新都桥</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>却让我大开眼界。沿途，各种条件的客栈宾馆应有尽有，还有帐篷营地随你选择。<br>揽客的店小二，在路边殷勤地舞动着手里的各式招牌，试图吸引住往来车辆留宿。一路嚷嚷着住宿难的我，被现状啪啪地扇了好几大嘴巴！哎哟喂！疼啊......<br>办理完入住已是21:00点将过，<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14727.html\" data-kw=\"新都桥\" target=\"_blank\">新都桥</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>的马路上，依旧人来车往好不热闹。看到宾馆斜对面，有一家名为“蜀香川菜”的小食店生意<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/34594.html\" data-kw=\"兴隆\" target=\"_blank\">兴隆</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，懒得走远，两个人花费94元点了一锅小份荤豆花，沾着酱料吃得热热络络，倦意全无。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/886837870.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/39/C1/CoUBGV2oj7qAE5KIABvU0bWG7Oo89.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/39/C1/CoUBGV2oj7qAE5KIABvU0bWG7Oo89.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/39/C1/CoUBGV2oj7qAE5KIABvU0bWG7Oo89.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"886837870\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6018060.html\" data-poiid=\"6018060\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">新都桥</a></p><p data-seq=\"886837882\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">马路边，水果车上卖的苹果和脆红李10元\\斤，不讲价。估摸着，平日里应该不是这个价格。听口音，小老板是蜀中来高原做生意的。大过节的，大家都不容易，买些吧。<br>原计划次日住<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10509.html\" data-kw=\"理塘\" target=\"_blank\">理塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>县城，行程时间比较宽裕，回宾馆后，向老板问询客房的WIFI密码，又随口问了周边哪里适合拍照。老板说:“如果再过十来天，这里哪儿哪儿都适合，但是现在嘛，稍微早了些”。此时，闲坐大厅沙发上的一人接过话头:“去鱼子西吧，现在，只有那边才有黄叶，你们明天上午八九点钟过去比较好。”</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10374/scenery_17448130/889253016.html\"><img src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9E/6E/CoUBGV2qddiALyxGABXkMGNrtyU63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9E/6E/CoUBGV2qddiALyxGABXkMGNrtyU63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s15/M00/9E/6E/CoUBGV2qddiALyxGABXkMGNrtyU63.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"889253016\" alt=\"\" class=\"fr-fin\"></a></p><p data-seq=\"889253018\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">谢过以后，回房休息，我曾有过多次<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144126.html\" data-kw=\"上高\" target=\"_blank\">上高</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>原的经历，压根儿没担心过高反。不知道哪根筋不对，睡下后就开始头疼、呕吐、失眠，折腾了半天，大约断断续续只睡了不足四个小时。<br><br>D2：<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14727.html\" data-kw=\"新都桥\" target=\"_blank\">新都桥</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>-<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62950.html\" data-kw=\"雅江\" target=\"_blank\">雅江</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>-<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10509.html\" data-kw=\"理塘\" target=\"_blank\">理塘</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>-铁匠山-喇嘛垭乡-<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10374.html\" data-kw=\"格聂\" target=\"_blank\">格聂</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>之眼龙金格登山居<br>10月3日，睡到自然醒也不过8:00点，到宾馆一楼吃过早餐，退房离店时，意外获赠了一瓶罐装氧气。琢磨着，虽曾多次经过<span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14727.html\" data-kw=\"新都桥\" target=\"_blank\">新都桥</a><span data-fr-verified=\"true\">&nbsp;</span>，都仅是路过而已，没认真玩过，索性干脆听人劝，走一趟鱼子西去了个到此一游的心愿。</p>', '5', '特别策划', '1', '2022-06-02', '10', '1000', '一个人', '2022-06-05 16:53:54');
